				RAILLY
		That would explain the bruises, I
		guess.  The struggle.

				FRANKI
		You want to go in?  Examine him?

				RAILLY
		Yes, please.  You said he gave a name...

				FRANKI
			(unlocking the door)
		James Cole.  That's everything we got.  None
