		No license, no prints, no warrants.  Nothing.
		You want me to go in with you?

				RAILLY
			(entering)
		No, thank you.

				FRANKI
		I'll be right here...just in case.

	INT.  ISOLATION CELL

	COLE stares at RAILLY.  The environment is intensely real...vivid
